- I’m not jealous.

00:47:19.680 --> 00:47:20.880
I just want to know why

00:47:20.920 --> 00:47:22.600
you had to walk that girl home too.

00:47:23.040 --> 00:47:25.000
And why I have to go through this again.

00:47:26.480 --> 00:47:28.000
I really don’t understand.

00:47:29.480 --> 00:47:31.280
How did you do that, May?

00:47:31.760 --> 00:47:33.280
Wanneung.

00:47:33.480 --> 00:47:35.000
You can do it too.

00:47:35.080 --> 00:47:36.880
Did you see her technique just now?

00:47:37.200 --> 00:47:38.280
I’m still amazed.

00:47:38.280 --> 00:47:39.880
Food support is here.

00:47:39.920 --> 00:47:40.920
I’ll help carry it.

00:47:42.880 --> 00:47:44.480
Wanneung, you’ve got this.

00:47:44.480 --> 00:47:46.040
Do your best, food’s waiting.

00:47:46.080 --> 00:47:47.800
- Okay.
- Okay.

00:47:49.160 --> 00:47:50.640
Watch the technique and follow it.

00:47:50.640 --> 00:47:51.680
I’m counting on you, May.

00:47:51.680 --> 00:47:52.800
Got it.

00:47:54.680 --> 00:47:56.360
The lines are pretty long.

00:47:56.400 --> 00:47:57.880
Like right now, we want to know

00:47:57.920 --> 00:47:58.920
why you walked her home.

00:47:59.680 --> 00:48:01.680
I just want to ask her—

00:49:05.280 --> 00:49:06.280
Cut.

00:49:10.160 --> 00:49:11.280
Cut the camera.

00:49:14.680 --> 00:49:16.080
I’ve been waiting for this.

00:49:16.280 --> 00:49:17.680
Great job.

00:49:22.880 --> 00:49:26.120
P’ Tong, how does it feel
partnering with overseas investors?

00:49:34.000 --> 00:49:35.600
- Wanneung.
- Yes?

00:49:36.400 --> 00:49:37.400
Are you nervous?

00:49:41.880 --> 00:49:43.120
Your hands are so cold.

00:49:43.160 --> 00:49:45.080
You’re not going to faint, right?

00:49:45.680 --> 00:49:47.840
If I faint, you have to catch me.

00:49:47.880 --> 00:49:49.960
Don’t let me collapse in front of the press.

00:49:50.000 --> 00:49:51.600
That would be so embarrassing.

00:49:52.320 --> 00:49:53.480
Okay.

00:50:10.080 --> 00:50:11.480
So cute.

00:50:12.560 --> 00:50:14.160
Amazing.

00:50:14.160 --> 00:50:15.480
Can you move a bit closer?

00:50:16.200 --> 00:50:18.360
- A little closer together.
- A little closer.

00:50:18.960 --> 00:50:20.960
- So cute.
- Give me a smile.

00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:22.800
Great. Beautiful.

00:50:23.240 --> 00:50:25.280
Lean in a bit, nice and close.

00:50:29.680 --> 00:50:30.800
Wanneung,

00:50:30.840 --> 00:50:32.280
how do you feel

00:50:32.280 --> 00:50:34.480
