00:50:34.800 --> 00:50:36.280
I’m really excited.

00:50:36.280 --> 00:50:38.080
It’s my very first movie.

00:50:38.120 --> 00:50:39.760
But I gave it my all.

00:50:39.800 --> 00:50:41.680
I hope everyone likes it.

00:50:44.960 --> 00:50:46.960
I wouldn’t be here today

00:50:47.000 --> 00:50:48.400
without P’ Tong giving me this chance.

00:50:48.440 --> 00:50:50.560
and guiding me throughout the shoot.

00:50:50.600 --> 00:50:52.600
And another important person

00:50:52.600 --> 00:50:53.600
is...

00:50:55.480 --> 00:50:56.600
Come on.

00:50:56.640 --> 00:50:58.600
- Come on.
- What do you mean?

00:50:58.600 --> 00:50:59.600
Win.

00:50:59.640 --> 00:51:01.280
who’s been such a great partner

00:51:01.320 --> 00:51:04.600
always supporting and encouraging me.

00:51:05.680 --> 00:51:08.000
