00:53:07.513 --> 00:53:09.033
That’s not enough.

00:54:10.553 --> 00:54:11.833
Let me help.

00:54:29.033 --> 00:54:30.553
Well done.

00:54:35.353 --> 00:54:36.753
Are you nervous?

00:54:38.273 --> 00:54:39.313
Yes.

00:54:42.833 --> 00:54:43.833
It’s okay.

00:54:43.873 --> 00:54:45.033
You can do it.

00:54:45.073 --> 00:54:46.273
Of course.

00:54:49.153 --> 00:54:50.233
Take a deep breath.

00:54:50.353 --> 00:54:51.753
Remember what I taught you?

00:55:05.033 --> 00:55:06.393
How is it? Better?

00:55:06.513 --> 00:55:07.513
Gam.

00:55:07.953 --> 00:55:09.233
