00:55:12.393 --> 00:55:13.633
Congratulations.

00:55:13.633 --> 00:55:14.953
Thank you.

00:55:15.633 --> 00:55:17.353
Congratulations, Win.

00:55:17.353 --> 00:55:18.553
Thank you.

00:55:18.633 --> 00:55:20.953
Aren’t you staying for the fan meet?

00:55:21.073 --> 00:55:23.073
