00:56:24.833 --> 00:56:27.193
It’s okay, I don’t want to trouble you.

00:56:27.233 --> 00:56:28.833
Don’t worry about it.

00:56:28.833 --> 00:56:31.593
Tom loves helping people,

00:56:31.633 --> 00:56:33.033
