00:56:33.073 --> 00:56:35.153
and... he’s single.

00:56:40.033 --> 00:56:41.433
Go on, Tom.

00:56:41.833 --> 00:56:43.153
I’ll give you a ride.

00:56:45.233 --> 00:56:46.313
Alright.

00:56:46.673 --> 00:56:47.673
I’ll go now.

00:56:48.713 --> 00:56:49.753
Bye-bye, Gam.

00:56:53.833 --> 00:56:55.393
Trying to play matchmaker?

00:56:55.633 --> 00:56:56.753
I’ll get you back for this.

00:56:59.433 --> 00:57:00.753
This way.

00:57:01.153 --> 00:57:02.473
I know.

00:57:05.833 --> 00:57:07.553
Hey, wait.

00:57:07.833 --> 00:57:08.873
Not you.

00:57:10.033 --> 00:57:13.113
- I’ll grab some food support first.
- Tom.

00:57:13.433 --> 00:57:14.873
Tom.

00:57:15.553 --> 00:57:17.553
Make it one box.

00:57:21.353 --> 00:57:24.353
Hello, I’m Win.

00:57:26.113 --> 00:57:29.433
Hello, I’m Wanneung.

00:57:40.113 --> 00:57:41.473
That was beautiful.

00:57:42.353 --> 00:57:43.633
So pretty.

00:58:57.313 --> 00:58:59.553
