00:59:40.633 --> 00:59:42.073
Was it sweet today, everyone?

00:59:42.073 --> 00:59:43.353
Sweet!

00:59:44.033 --> 00:59:45.073
So sweet, right?

00:59:45.073 --> 00:59:46.313
Alright, everyone.

00:59:46.313 --> 00:59:48.073
Before we move on to

00:59:48.113 --> 00:59:49.393
