00:59:51.153 --> 00:59:52.273
to say a few words

00:59:52.313 --> 00:59:54.153
to the fans. Please.

00:59:54.753 --> 00:59:55.753
Okay.

00:59:55.833 --> 00:59:57.793
I’d like to thank

00:59:57.833 --> 00:59:59.713
all the fans

00:59:59.753 --> 01:00:01.233
for coming to see us today.

01:00:01.233 --> 01:00:02.633
Thank you for loving

01:00:02.673 --> 01:00:04.513
and supporting us.

01:00:04.513 --> 01:00:06.193
I promise

01:00:06.233 --> 01:00:07.593
to stay dedicated

01:00:07.593 --> 01:00:09.513
and give my best in every work.

01:00:09.513 --> 01:00:11.233
so it turns out as best as possible.

01:00:11.513 --> 01:00:12.913
So that all the fans

01:00:12.953 --> 01:00:14.553
can enjoy it.

01:00:14.993 --> 01:00:17.153
