01:00:27.673 --> 01:00:28.753
Please.

01:00:52.193 --> 01:00:54.833
Everything that happened today

01:00:55.513 --> 01:00:58.033
is more than I ever dreamed of.

01:01:00.713 --> 01:01:03.153
Being able to stand here

01:01:04.153 --> 01:01:06.233
wasn’t easy at all.

01:01:06.913 --> 01:01:07.993
I had to put in

01:01:08.033 --> 01:01:09.953
so much effort.

01:01:09.993 --> 01:01:11.633
Before this,

01:01:11.633 --> 01:01:13.833
I failed every audition.

01:01:14.153 --> 01:01:16.553
I got eliminated from singing contests too.

01:01:16.633 --> 01:01:17.913
But I never gave up

01:01:17.953 --> 01:01:19.673
trying.

01:01:19.713 --> 01:01:21.233
Until one day,

01:01:21.633 --> 01:01:23.433
I was given a great opportunity

01:01:23.633 --> 01:01:25.153
to act in a film.

01:01:25.833 --> 01:01:27.033
I tried

01:01:27.073 --> 01:01:29.473
my best every single day

01:01:29.833 --> 01:01:32.033
so that I wouldn’t feel

01:01:32.473 --> 01:01:34.633
and regret it later.

01:01:36.113 --> 01:01:38.033
But today,

01:01:42.393 --> 01:01:44.713
when I look back,

01:01:47.633 --> 01:01:49.153
I feel like

01:01:49.953 --> 01:01:52.153
I have no regrets at all.

01:02:15.833 --> 01:02:18.353
Win once told me that

01:02:20.353 --> 01:02:22.033
if one day

01:02:22.833 --> 01:02:25.033
I have fans,

01:02:26.633 --> 01:02:28.953
I have to take good care of them,

01:02:29.953 --> 01:02:31.753
love them as much as I can,

01:02:32.553 --> 01:02:34.833
to match how much they love me.

01:02:35.913 --> 01:02:38.353
I love you all so much.

01:02:58.753 --> 01:02:59.953
Win, Wanneung.

01:02:59.993 --> 01:03:01.593
Win, Wanneung.

