01:06:49.753 --> 01:06:51.233
I’m sorry.

01:06:51.273 --> 01:06:52.433
We’ll be away all week,

01:06:52.473 --> 01:06:53.633
I was worried the cactus might die,

01:06:53.673 --> 01:06:54.793
